freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: So  i tested on rhe 29th, the same day I got my vaccine shot. That test came back positive. My test on the 28rh AND the 30th were negative.  I am waiting for results for the 31st. (As I work in several different SNFs, i follow each of  their schedules for testing) So now i have to quarantine until January 9. I don't have and have never had any symptoms.  I get screened every day. Wondering if a false positive.
